            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>finely sliced chilli</strong> with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong> in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>quick-pickled chillies</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and cut into quarters, lengthways</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1666707896501-x200.jpg",
