    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pulled pork enchiladas</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>tangy mayo</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>quick-pickled chillies </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Serve the<strong> lettuce wedges </strong>to the side and top with the <strong>salsa fresca</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
